{"aid": "iwc8ho68gwz1ol", "result": {"status": "active", "unique_views": 32, "request_instructor_me": false, "change_log": [{"type": "create", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-10-09T02:28:37Z", "data": "iu20gba8sh02u2", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie"}, {"to": "iu20gba6dmu2u1", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-10-09T02:31:06Z", "type": "followup", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie"}, {"to": "iu20gba6dmu2u1", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-10-10T16:19:02Z", "type": "followup", "uid": "illojz7yoPj"}, {"to": "iu20gba6dmu2u1", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-12-05T11:29:55Z", "type": "followup", "uid": "ivste75wdW6"}], "upvote_ids": [], "id": "iu20gba6dmu2u1", "bookmarked": 5, "tags": ["instructor-note", "lecture1"], "i_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "children": [{"folders": [], "updated": "2016-10-09T02:31:06Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "created": "2016-10-09T02:31:06Z", "type": "followup", "no_answer": 0, "id": "iu20jiik9iy5bj", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Week 10/9 - 10/15", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 13, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>段机制是CPU、操作系统和编译器一起合作来支持用户编程的。为了让用户只管逻辑地址&#xff0c;操作系统和编译器需要在CPU硬件的支持下&#xff0c;实现逻辑地址到物理地址的映射。</p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-10-10T16:19:02Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "illojz7yoPj", "created": "2016-10-10T16:19:02Z", "type": "followup", "no_answer": 0, "id": "iu49k3isbhi4u7", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Week 10/9 - 10/15", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 13, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>自己的理解是 &#xff1a; 如果是建立在操作系统之上的用户编程&#xff0c;那么我们基本上是不用考虑段机制的&#xff0c;和我们有交集的地址只是逻辑地址。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>但如果是站在操作系统这一层去编程&#xff0c;涉及到的地址会从 逻辑地址 到 线性地址 再到物理地址&#xff0c;这时候我们都需要进行考虑了。</p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-12-05T11:29:55Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "ivste75wdW6", "created": "2016-12-05T11:29:55Z", "type": "followup", "no_answer": 0, "id": "iwbzvzzh8gp3au", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>物理地址空间的连续和非连续&#xff0c;对物理内存管理有直接的影响&#xff0c;物理内存管理的实现依赖于计算机的内存架构&#xff0c;对于OS而言&#xff0c;内存管理的很大一部分是物理内存管理。</p>"}], "nr": 939, "bucket_order": 2, "type": "note", "folders": ["lecture1"], "no_answer_followup": 0, "num_favorites": 1, "bucket_name": "Today", "q_edits": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "request_instructor": 0, "created": "2016-10-09T02:28:37Z", "is_tag_good": false, "config": {}, "s_edits": [], "my_favorite": false, "default_anonymity": "no", "t": 1480951844000, "tag_good": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "history": [{"content": "<p>\n</p><div>\n<h1></h1>\n<p>question 被 <a href=\"http://www.xuetangx.com/courses/course-v1:TsinghuaX&#43;30240243X&#43;sp/discussion/forum/users/327774\">XupeiD</a> 发布</p>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<ul><li><a href=\"http://www.xuetangx.com/courses/course-v1:TsinghuaX&#43;30240243X&#43;sp/discussion/forum/i4x-TsinghuaX-30240243X-course-2015_T1/threads/57ea0980459f083be4009a38\">投票已有 0 个投票0 票 </a></li><li>关注关注 </li><li>\n<div>更多 </div>\n</li></ul>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n<p>为什么说段机制是为了用户编程&#xff0c;编程只要管逻辑地址就行啊&#xff0c;为什么还要管映射到物理内存之后是离散的还是聚集的。</p>\n</div>", "anon": "no", "created": "2016-10-09T02:28:37Z", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "subject": "关于段机制的问题"}]}, "error": null}